originalText.text: Not even sure what I was doing yet circumstances led me to David's reading, and aren't I glad now.. David is super nice and patient. His reading is extremely accurate. He also helped me with spiritual energy cleaning. Before the work, he patiently explained everything. During the process and after, he carefully provided feedback and guidance. I really can't thank him enough for everything. I would recommend him and I myself will come back to him.

originalText.text: I got a reading from David and let me tell you! I was impressed and it was worth it.  David was also super patient and understanding.  There was no rush which I enjoyed the most, as you can’t put a time limit, as every person is different.  I liked that a lot. David reading my cards was clear and explained thoroughly to the point that I didn’t  have many questions to ask because the read was really impeccable. He helped me and provided guidance, with his services I felt at  peace, serene, and content.  I do not regret reaching out to David.  If I had to do it again, I will, without a doubt contact David.  I would recommend David to all my friends and family and anyone who is seeking to get a very good read.  I will be honest, before David, I did get a few readings and after I got a read from David, the want or the need to get another read was gone. I was fulfilled with the  services provided by David, for me that means and says a lot.
